'''柱頭'''（{{lang-en|stigma}}）位於[[花|花]]的[[心皮|心皮]]（或多個心皮愈合）的頂端，以[[花柱|花柱]]連接[[子房|子房]]。[[傳粉|傳粉]]時[[花粉|花粉]]落到柱頭上，並萌發出[[花粉管|花粉管]]以到達[[胚珠|胚珠]]。柱頭通常具有粘性，並演化出各種不同有利於接受花粉的形式<ref>''The Penguin Dictionary of Botany'', edited by Elizabeth Toothill, Penguin Books 1984 ISBN 0-14-051126-1</ref>，花粉可能透過風傳遞到柱頭（[[風媒傳粉|風媒傳粉]]），也可能透過動物或水流。

柱頭的外形變異很大，有細長型或圓形，並可能具有毛。當花粉離開[[花藥|花葯]]時，通常是呈脫水狀態，抵達柱頭後柱頭有助花粉濕潤並萌發花粉管<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.plantcell.org/content/16/suppl_1/S84.full |author=Anna F. Edlund, Robert Swanson and Daphne Preuss |year=2004 |title=Pollen and stigma structure and function: the role of diversity in pollination |journal=Plant Cell |volume=16 |issue=Supplement |pages=84-97 |doi=10.1105/tpc.015800 |access-date=2015-01-21 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930151048/http://www.plantcell.org/content/16/suppl_1/S84.full |dead-url=no }}</ref>。柱頭可以確保萌發的花粉屬於同[[種_(生物)|種]]植物，還可以執行[[孢子體|孢子體]][[自交不親和性|自交不親和性]]，避免基因型太接近的花粉萌發出花粉管，以[[蕓薹屬|蕓薹屬]]植物為例，花粉壁具有S基因的產物SCR<ref>{{cite journal |author=Schopfer, C. R., M. E. Nasrallah, and J. B. Nasrallah |title=The male determinant of self-incompatibility in Brassica |journal=Science |volume=286 | doi = 10.1126/science.286.5445.1697  |pages=1697–1700 |year=1999 |issue=5445 |pmid=10576728 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1073/pnas.040556397 |author=Takayama, S., H. Shiba, M. Iwano, H. Shimosato, F.-S. Che, N. Kai, M. Watanabe, G. Suzuki, K. Hinata, and A. Isogai |title=The pollen determinant of self-incompatibility in Brassica campestris |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. |volume=97 |issue=4 |pages=1920–5 |year=2000 |pmid=10677556 |pmc=26537 }}</ref> （皆為富含[[半胱胺酸|半胱胺酸]]的蛋白質），S基因可能具有高達百種基因型，彼此間有漸進的顯隱性關係。柱頭則具有稱為SRK的[[膜蛋白|膜蛋白]]，在胞內有[[激酶|激酶]]的活性區域<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1073/pnas.88.19.8816 |author=Stein, J. C., B. Howlett, D. C. Boyes, M. E. Nasrallah, and J. B. Nasrallah |title=Molecular cloning of a putative receptor protein kinase gene encoded at the self-incompatibility locus of Brassica oleracea |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. |volume=88 |issue=19 |pages=8816–20 |year=1991 |pmid=1681543 |pmc=52601 }}: .</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Nasrallah, J. B., and M. E. Nasrallah |title=Pollen–stigma signalling in the sporophytic self-incompatibility response |journal=Pl. Cell |volume=5 |pages=1325–35 |year=1993 |doi=10.2307/3869785}}</ref>，不同種SRK是不同種SCR的[[受體|受體]]。另外柱頭還產生一種稱為SLG的蛋白質，該蛋白與SRK序列類似，可能是SCR的共同受器，用以增強訊號<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1038/35002628 |author=Takasaki, T., K. Hatakeyama, G. Suzuki, M. Watanabe, A. Isogai, and K. Hinata |title=The S receptor kinase determines self-incompatibility in ''Brassica stigma'' |journal=Nature |volume=403 |issue=6772 |pages=913–6 |year=2000 |pmid=10706292 }}</ref>當SRK與SCR配對時，會使SRK的激酶區域{{link-en|自體磷酸化|Autophosphorylation}}，並經過尚不清楚的下游途徑傳遞訊息，阻止花粉管萌發<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1104/pp.124.3.935 |author=Schopfer, C. R., and J. B. Nasrallah |title=Self-incompatibility. Prospects for a novel putative peptide-signaling molecule |journal=Pl. Physiol.  |volume=124 |pages=935–9 |year=2000 |issue=3 }}</ref>。

